<ul style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;"><li style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">John is making a claim that these words are God breathed and are a direct message from Him through John.</li>
<li style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">Light is something that we humans have still no conceivable way to drown out or put out. Darkness is essentially the absence of light.</li>
<li style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">This description of God as light is making the claim that God is infinite and impossible to put out. He is a source of light that illuminates and eliminates all darkness in sight.</li></ul></body></html>